SUMMARY:OV Coached Pickleball (60m) - James
DESCRIPTION:Instructor: James Cole\nRoom: OV Pickle East 1\, 2\nLocati
 on: Ocotillo Village\nPickleball Coaching is now at the Ocotillo Vill
 age every Sunday. Open to all player levels who are needing or wantin
 g some extra coaching\, to sharpen there game play.\n\nSunday Group C
 oached Sessions will run $30pp from 10-11am\n\nFollowed by Free Open 
 play for anyone 11am to 1pm\n\nRegular Open Play will also continue o
 n week days on Tuesday and Thursday's\, Alternating each week from 1:
 00PM Noon to 3:00PM. \n\n3 Courts will be available on the Basketball
  Court. The Basketball Court will not be open for for Basketball play
  until after 1pm on Sundays and after 3pm on Tuesdays and Thursdays.\
 n\nCourt rotation is available based on first come\, first serve basi
 s. Rules and Play Policy will be posted at the Court.\n\n*There will 
 be no Officials. Honesty and Good Sportsmanship will be expected at a
 ll times.
END:VEVENT
