DESCRIPTION:Instructor: James Cole\nRoom: OV Pickle East 1\, 2\; OV Pi
 ckle West 1\, 2\nLocation: Ocotillo Village\nPickleball is available 
 at Ocotillo Village.  Every Tuesday and Thursday each week from 1:00P
 M to 3:00PM and every Sunday 10am to 1pm on the Weekends.  \n\n4 Cour
 ts are available for all player levels who want to have a fun\, socia
 lize and recreational play.\n\nCertified Pickleball Coach\, James Col
 e will be providing Coaching and Instruction for those who are needin
 g or wanting some extra instruction or 1 on 1 Coaching.\n\nThe Basket
 ball Court will not be open for for Basketball play until after the S
 cheduled Pickleball Open Play Times are over.\n\nPlay time is reserve
 d for the first 20 that register on the Village Mobile App.  Registra
 tion opens 48 hours prior to the day and time of the next scheduled P
 ickleball Open Play.   Rules and Play Policy will be posted at the Co
 urt.\n\n*There will be no Officials. Honesty and Good Sportsmanship w
 ill be expected at all times.
END:VEVENT
