 n your body through passive stretching. The postures are usually adap
 ted from supine or seated yoga poses with the addition of blocks\, bo
 lsters\, and blankets to eliminate unnecessary straining. * Suitable 
 for all Levels of Fitness Intensity Rating \n\nPlease sign up on the 
